---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '@/components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '@/components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy — ProxyCraft" noindex>
  <Header />
  <main class="pt-28 pb-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <div class="prose-invert mt-8 space-y-6 text-text-muted">
        <p>Last updated: March 2026</p>
        <p>
          This Privacy Policy describes what data ProxyCraft ("Operator", "we") collects and
          processes, and how we use and protect it. By using the service, you agree to the terms
          of this policy.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">1. About Us</h2>
        <p>
          ProxyCraft is a service providing secure internet connection services (VPN, Telegram
          Proxy, WhatsApp Proxy). The Operator strives to collect only the minimum data necessary
          for the service to operate, and does not use it for commercial purposes beyond service
          delivery.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">2. Data We Collect</h2>
        <p>During your use of the service, we may collect the following data:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc space-y-1 pl-6">
          <li>
            <strong class="text-text">Telegram identifiers</strong> — Telegram ID, username, display
            name — for account creation and identification.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong class="text-text">Payment data</strong> — transaction details, payment history.
            We do not store full bank card details — these are processed by payment providers.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong class="text-text">Technical information</strong> — device type, operating system,
            client app version, platform.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong class="text-text">Service usage data</strong> — subscription details, activated
            configurations, activation and expiry dates.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong class="text-text">Website analytics</strong> — cookies, IP addresses, browser
            information, and on-site behavior (via Yandex.Metrica analytics).
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">3. What We Do NOT Collect or Do</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc space-y-1 pl-6">
          <li>We do not log internet traffic or store the contents of transmitted data.</li>
          <li>We do not track websites or services visited by users.</li>
          <li>We do not store connection history (time, duration, sources).</li>
          <li>We do not sell, rent, or exchange personal data with third parties for marketing purposes.</li>
          <li>We do not disclose personal data to government agencies without a lawful request.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">4. Purposes of Data Processing</h2>
        <p>Collected data is used exclusively for:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc space-y-1 pl-6">
          <li>Providing the service and technical support.</li>
          <li>Managing accounts, subscriptions, and payments.</li>
          <li>Sending subscription notifications via Telegram bot.</li>
          <li>Improving service quality and detecting issues.</li>
          <li>Complying with applicable legal requirements.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">5. Cookies and Analytics</h2>
        <p>
          Our website uses Yandex.Metrica web analytics to analyze traffic. Yandex.Metrica
          collects anonymized data about user behavior: pages viewed, referral sources, time
          on site. Data is transferred to Yandex and processed according to their privacy policy.
        </p>
        <p>
          For more details, see our{' '}
          <a href="/en/cookies" class="text-accent hover:underline">Cookie Policy</a>.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">6. Third-Party Data Sharing</h2>
        <p>We do not share your data with third parties, except in the following cases:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc space-y-1 pl-6">
          <li>
            <strong class="text-text">Payment processors</strong> — when processing payments,
            your data is handled by payment providers (Telegram Payments, etc.) per their policies.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong class="text-text">Cloud infrastructure</strong> — data may be processed on
            cloud provider servers under data processing agreements.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong class="text-text">Legal requirements</strong> — upon a lawful request from
            authorized authorities.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">7. Data Storage and Security</h2>
        <p>
          We take reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect your data from
          unauthorized access, modification, disclosure, or destruction. Data is stored on
          secured servers. Payment data is not stored on our servers — it is processed directly
          by payment providers.
        </p>
        <p>
          Personal data is retained for the duration of account activity and deleted upon user
          request or after 3 years of account inactivity.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">8. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc space-y-1 pl-6">
          <li>Request information about what data we hold about you.</li>
          <li>Request correction of inaccurate data.</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your personal data.</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent to data processing.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          To exercise these rights, contact{' '}
          <a href="mailto:support@proxycraft.tech" class="text-accent hover:underline">
            support@proxycraft.tech
          </a>.
          Requests are processed within 30 days.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">9. Policy Changes</h2>
        <p>
          The Operator may update this policy. Users are notified of material changes via
          Telegram bot or upon next login. The current version is always available on this page.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text">10. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For privacy and data protection inquiries:
          <a href="mailto:support@proxycraft.tech" class="text-accent hover:underline ml-1">
            support@proxycraft.tech
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
